Name: Atlanticus Holdings Corporation 9.25% Senior Notes due 2029
Description: Atlanticus Holdings Corporation is a financial services firm dedicated to delivering innovative credit and financing solutions to underserved consumer markets. The company issues 9.25% Senior Notes due 2029, utilizing the proceeds to bolster its diverse portfolio of credit offerings. By harnessing advanced technology and proprietary analytics, Atlanticus not only enhances customer engagement but also effectively manages risk and capital dynamics. With a strong focus on financial inclusion, Atlanticus is strategically positioned to leverage growth opportunities in the evolving credit landscape.
